snippet.title: Amber Alert for abducted 11 year old from Peel Region OPP COMMS.  Feb 14-15, 2019
snippet.description:
I was watching youtube as i heard my cell phone make an Amber alert about a missing 11 year old.  I quickly turned on my scanner and recorded.   
The OPP pinged his cell and it last pinged in Pickering at Port Union and 401 hiway around 9pm today.
Later a vehicle driving north on hiway 400 spotted the suspect vehicle in question and OPP came from Barrie and Orillia. townships.
The OPP did a high risk take down.
Vehicle seized and OPP in Communication now with Peel police.

This was an abduction but on the radio the dispatcher advised the suspect is wanted for Homicide.    

Child found dead in a Brampton home.    

Last 10 minutes of the COMMS are quiet but i was recording, you can skip it.   No time to edit.    This is in real time COMMS.


Const. Akil Mooken said the pair were together to celebrate the daughter’s birthday but when the time came to bring her back to the mother, who has custody, they didn’t show up. Comments were made by Rajkumar to the mother indicating he could cause harm to himself and his daughter.

“We have concerns for both Riya and Roopesh,” Mooken said. “We are asking the public for assistance in helping to locate both of these individuals.”

Emergency Management Ontario followed Peel’s original report of the abduction with an emergency alert deployed to mobile devices just after 11:30 p.m.

Police said Roopesh Rajkumar is operating a silver, two-door Honda Civic with a plate number ARBV 598. They were last seen in the area of Hurontario Rd. and Derry Rd. in Mississauga.

Riya Rajkumar is described as brown, four feet, 60 lbs., thin build, with below shoulder length black hair. She was last wearing a pink dress with hearts, black boots, black tights, black jacket with fur-lined hood. She also has a black and white purse with a pink heart that has an R in it.

Peel police have confirmed they working with the Ontario Provincial Police on the investigation.


UPDATE.....

CHILD FOUND DEAD IN A BRAMPTON HOME...
